          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-198-700B-line-1" n="1">I often wish'<hi rend="superscript">d</hi> that I had clear</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-198-700B-line-2" n="2">For life six hundred pounds a year,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-198-700B-line-3" n="3">A handsome house to lodge a friend</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-198-700B-line-4" n="4">A river at my garden's end.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-198-700B-line-5" n="5">A terras walk &amp; half a rood</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-198-700B-line-6" n="6">Of land set out to plant a wood.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-198-700B-line-7" n="7">Well, now I have all this, &amp; more,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-198-700B-line-8" n="8">I ask not to increase my Store</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-198-700B-line-9" n="9">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-198-700B-line-10" n="10">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-198-700B-line-11" n="11">om.</l>
